features.title: 24/7 email & phone support
features.description: Award winning, global, 24/7/365 email & emergency phone support (Enterprise plans). Plus on-demand resources, guides & best practice implementation.

features.title: Massive network scale
features.description: Our global network spans over %{DataCenterCount} cities & %{CountryCount} countries. Operating within %{OperationMilliseconds} milliseconds of 95% of the Internet-connected population globally.

features.title: Ease of use & guided setup
features.description: No code changes; the Cloudflare dashboard enables quick configuration. Enterprise guided onboarding, training & continued 24/7/365 support.

features.title: 100% uptime reliability
features.description: Network prioritization exclusive to Cloudflare Enterprise plans. Dependable service level agreements (SLA) with 100% uptime & reliable service you can trust.

relatedBlades.title: Trusted by the biggest brands worldwide
relatedBlades.copy: Cloudflare named a 2022 Gartner® Peer Insights™ Customers' Choice for  CDN<sup>1</sup>.

relatedBlades.title: Secure your workforce, anywhere & everywhere
relatedBlades.copy:
No matter where they're working, your workforce requires secure access to internal applications and tools. Cloudflare Zero Trust enables seamless, identity and software-defined security, allowing you to secure your remote teams, devices, and data. All without sacrificing performance or usability.
- Cloudflare named a "Representative Vendor" in the 2022 Gartner® "Market Guide for Zero Trust Network Access<sup>4</sup>
- Cloudflare named a "Leader" in KuppingerCole's Leadership Compass for Zero Trust Network Access, 2022<sup>6</sup>
relatedBlades.learnMoreText: Learn more about Zero Trust for Enterprises

relatedBlades.title: Make applications fast, available, & scalable
relatedBlades.copy:
With Cloudflare, rich web application experiences never come at the expense of security or performance. Since our network spans more than %{DataCenterCount} cities in over %{CountryCount} countries, we fight attacks and serve web requests closer to users.

- Cloudflare named a "Leader" in the [2022 IDC MarketScape for WW CDN Services](https://www.cloudflare.com/lp/idc-worldwide-cdn-marketscape/ "IDC MarketScape Leader")<sup>5</sup>
- Cloudflare named a 2022 Gartner® Peer Insights™ Customers' Choice for CDN<sup>2</sup> and WAAP<sup>3</sup>
relatedBlades.learnMoreText: Learn more about Application Security & Performance
relatedBlades.subheadline: Improved application performance means a better user experience

relatedBlades.title: All-in-one solution for network security & scalability
relatedBlades.copy:
Networking solutions to help enterprises connect, secure, and accelerate their corporate networks. Without the cost or complexity of legacy network hardware. Upgrade to a single global network with built-in, software-defined [Zero Trust](https://www.cloudflare.com/learning/security/glossary/what-is-zero-trust/) services, DDoS mitigation, firewalls, and traffic acceleration.
- Cloudflare named a "Leader" - [2021 Forrester Wave™: DDoS Mitigation Solutions](https://www.cloudflare.com/forrester-wave-ddos-mitigation-2021/ "Cloudflare 'Leader' in Forrester Wave DDoS mitigation")<sup>1</sup>
- A global network in over %{DataCenterCount} cities & over %{CountryCount} countries
relatedBlades.learnMoreText: Learn more about Network Security for Enterprises
relatedBlades.subheadline: Unified layered security across all endpoints & users

relatedBlades.title: Built for enterprises large and small
relatedBlades.copy: Cloudflare provides the services that were once only available to Internet giants and makes them available to everyone. Our flexible and programmable global network was built to serve companies and organizations of all sizes - from individual developers to large corporations. We deploy products that are easy to use, continuously improved, and cost effective.

relatedBlades.quote: The support with Cloudflare is great. It feels like we're working with another HubSpot team. They really seem to care, they take things seriously. I've filed cases and gotten responses back in under a minute. The quality of the responses is just a night and day difference.

quoteCarousel.quote: "Cloudflare wins on its smart and scalable solutions, as well as its impressive customer support. Unlike local partners whose support desks operate on office hours, Cloudflare gives us round-the-clock support."

Before Cloudflare, our customers in China experienced a significant lag-time for updates to their wearable products. After becoming a Cloudflare customer, our devices updated much faster in China. This was an important enhancement to the user experience for our customers.

marketoEmbeddedForm.bladeName: Enterprise HUB - Enterprise Demo Us Form (1341)

features.title: 24/7/365 support via chat, email, and phone
features.description: Phone, chat, and email support with median response time of 15 minutes. For critical business issues, Enterprise customers have access to our 24/7/365 emergency phone support hotline.

features.title: 100% uptime guarantee with 25x reimbursement SLA
features.description: In the rare event of downtime, Enterprise customers receive a 25x credit against the monthly fee, in proportion to the respective disruption and affected customer ratio.

features.title: Predictable flat-rate pricing for usage based products
features.description: Only enterprise customers can negotiate flat rate pricing on Argo, Rate limiting, Workers, Load Balancing, Live Stream and more.

features.title: Advanced Cache controls
features.description: Enterprise customers have lower TTLs and can purge cache by tag or host.

features.title: Bot management
features.description: Use the power of Cloudflare's network to intelligently manage bot traffic to your application in order to prevent credential stuffing, inventory hoarding, content scraping and other types of fraud.

features.title: Access to raw logs
features.description: Take charge of your data and run your own analytics using raw log data from web assets on Cloudflare's network.

features.title: Firewall analytics
features.description: Understand the impact of your WAF configuration. Firewall Analytics let you know if a rule is effective by illustrating the impact in an easy to digest format.

features.title: Role based access
features.description: Provide role-based access throughout your organization. Each user is given set permissions, individual API keys, and optional two-factor authentication.

features.title: Network prioritization
features.description: Enterprise web assets are placed on Cloudflare dedicated IP ranges, providing prioritized routing and protection to ensure maximum speed and availability.
